Since there is a 66% sale on lifetime ranks on Avicus, it's a must for me to do a giveaway.


Rules:

-2 winners will be picked.
-How to enter? Just post your name below.
-Winners will be picked on the 31st of October in the evening (European timezone).
-If you're already premium (Gold, Emerald or Diamond), you can enter for someone else, but nobody is allowed to enter twice. If someone's name is posted twice, the user only will be counted once and the second post is ignored.
-Please spell all names correctly!

Good luck :D
